T_2MC: Temperature at 2 meters above ground in Celsius
WSPD_100m: Absolute value of the wind speed in the height of 100 meters above ground in meters per second (m/s), i.e. regardless of its direction
TOT_PREC: Hourly total precipitation (e.g. rain, snow) in kilogram per square meter (kg/m²)
GLOB: Global radiation flux (ASWDIFD_S + ASWDIR_S) at the surface in Watt per square meter (W/m²)
